OL,3,CJeremy Kyle Show guest 'distraught'
OL,4,Cafter recording, landlady tells inquest
OL,6,FThe landlady of TV guest Steve Dymond
OL,7,Fhas told an inquest into his death
OL,8,Fthat he was "distraught" and a "broken
OL,9,Fman" after the recording of the Jeremy
OL,10,FKyle Show.
OL,12,FThe 63-year-old, from Portsmouth,
OL,13,FHampshire, is believed to have taken
OL,14,Fhis own life seven days after filming
OL,15,Ffor the ITV show in May 2019.
