OL,3,CJeremy Kyle Show guest 'distraught'
OL,4,Cafter recording, landlady tells inquest
OL,6,FThe Winchester inquest heard he was
OL,7,F"booed" by the audience during the
OL,8,Ffilming after a lie detector test
OL,9,Fsuggested he had been lying about
OL,10,Fhaving not cheated on his partner Jane
OL,11,FCallaghan.
OL,13,FMr Dymond had rung ITV 40 to 50 times
OL,14,Fin "desperate" attempts to become a
OL,15,Fguest on the show, the inquest
OL,16,Fpreviously heard.
