OL,3,CJeremy Kyle Show guest 'distraught'
OL,4,Cafter recording, landlady tells inquest
OL,6,FLandlady Michelle Thaxter told the
OL,7,Fhearing: "My connection to him, he
OL,8,Fcome to stay with us for a few weeks,
OL,9,Fhe was looking for somewhere to live,
OL,10,Fhe had split up from his partner and
OL,11,Fwe had a room."
OL,13,FShe said Mr Dymond had called her
OL,14,Fafter they had advertised the room,
OL,15,Fsaying he "was just a really, really
OL,16,Fnice guy".
OL,18,FMrs Thaxter added: "He said he had
OL,19,Fsplit up from his partner and he was
OL,20,Fstaying in a hotel, and it was costing
OL,21,Fhim a lot of money."
