OL,3,CJeremy Kyle Show guest 'distraught'
OL,4,Cafter recording, landlady tells inquest
OL,6,FHe said he wanted to go on the show
OL,7,F"because Jane thought he was sleeping
OL,8,For seeing some other woman, but he
OL,9,Fwanted to prove, tell her that he
OL,10,Fwasn't, my opinion, I don't think he
OL,11,Fwas.
OL,13,F"He really did love her but he wanted
OL,14,Fto prove to her that he wasn't lying."
OL,16,FShe continued: "All he wanted was to
OL,17,Fget back with this woman, he
OL,18,Fabsolutely loved her, he adored her."
