OL,3,CJeremy Kyle Show guest 'distraught'
OL,4,Cafter recording, landlady tells inquest
OL,6,FShe said Mr Dymond had told her the
OL,7,Faudience had "booed" him, adding: "He
OL,8,Fsaid 'Jeremy backed me into a corner'.
OL,9,FVery uncomfortable."
OL,11,FShe said Mr Dymond told her that he
OL,12,Fwas upset by "how he was treated on
OL,13,Fthe show, he was saying he had told
OL,14,Ftoo many lies".
OL,16,FShe added that she had told him to
OL,17,Ffocus on his son, who he had just
OL,18,Fbecome reconnected with and found out
OL,19,Fhe had three grandchildren.
