OL,11,FMental health help and support links:
OL,13,FMr Dymond had been diagnosed with a
OL,14,Fdepressive disorder in 1995 and had
OL,15,Ftaken overdoses on four occasions ` in
OL,16,FJanuary 1995, twice in December 2002
OL,17,Fand in April 2005, the court was told.
