OL,3,CJeremy Kyle Show guest 'distraught'
OL,4,Cafter recording, landlady tells inquest
OL,6,FAfter his first application to attend
OL,7,Fthe show was rejected because he had
OL,8,Fbeen diagnosed with depression and
OL,9,Fprescribed medication, Mr Dymond
OL,10,Fobtained a letter from his GP stating
OL,11,Fhe had not taken the medication and
OL,12,Fhis mood had improved.
OL,14,FHe was subsequently assessed by mental
OL,15,Fhealth nurse Steph MacDonald employed
OL,16,Fby the show as suitable to appear as
OL,17,Fhe had not "scored for depression" in
OL,18,Fher evaluation of him.
