OL,3,CJeremy Kyle Show guest 'distraught'
OL,4,Cafter recording, landlady tells inquest
OL,6,FMr Kyle defended his handling of Mr
OL,7,FDymond during the recording, saying he
OL,8,Fhad tried to "de-escalate" the
OL,9,Fsituation and added that the selection
OL,10,Fof guests and their aftercare "were
OL,11,Fnot my responsibility, I was the
OL,12,Fpresenter".
OL,14,FMrs Thaxter's son Sam Kendall said in
OL,15,Fa statement read to the hearing that
OL,16,FMs Callaghan had split from Mr Dymond
OL,17,Fbecause she "had found pictures on his
OL,18,Flaptop or computer that led her to
OL,19,Fbelieve he was cheating".
