OL,6,FMr Kendall said that Mr Dymond was in
OL,7,Fa "bad way" after the show recording
OL,8,Fand added: "Steve did tell me he was
OL,9,Fabsolutely mortified at the way Jeremy
OL,10,FKyle spoke to him on the show."
OL,12,FHe added that Mr Dymond was "kind and
OL,13,Fcaring and wouldn't hurt anyone".
